title: WEDNESDAY 5/12 - NFL SCHEDULE RELEASE DAY
itunes:title: WEDNESDAY 5/12 - NFL SCHEDULE RELEASE DAY
description:
It's finally here! The NFL Schedule release (0:08) is tonight at 8PM ET. Vikings receiver Adam Thielen (0:42) gives his thoughts on playing at Lambeau Field, meanwhile Packers wide receiver Davante Adams (1:40) says Aaron Rodgers future in Green Bay could also determine if he stays. Bucs GM Jason Licht (2:39) says Tom Brady could play until he's 50 years old. Teddy Bridgewater (3:22) ready to compete for the starting job in Denver...and Texans owner Cal McNair talks about the QB situation in Houston
